    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>钓鱼</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用船上的起重机捕捉汞合金</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072380/extras/fe3dcc34ea736a5c9c908153c192f264.poster.avif?t=1749983490\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072380/extras/fe3dcc34ea736a5c9c908153c192f264.webm?t=1749983490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072380/extras/fe3dcc34ea736a5c9c908153c192f264.mp4?t=1749983490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>捕获</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将汞齐储存在地窖中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072380/extras/e91dcf9170fd30e6aafe7a3a1b2e52ed.poster.avif?t=1749983490\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072380/extras/e91dcf9170fd30e6aafe7a3a1b2e52ed.webm?t=1749983490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072380/extras/e91dcf9170fd30e6aafe7a3a1b2e52ed.mp4?t=1749983490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>浏览</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乘坐渔船游览拉因斯塔拉松</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072380/extras/68c0cbfaae3472f1ae35b7890ee5d579.poster.avif?t=1749983490\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072380/extras/68c0cbfaae3472f1ae35b7890ee5d579.webm?t=1749983490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072380/extras/68c0cbfaae3472f1ae35b7890ee5d579.mp4?t=1749983490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一场神秘的事故之后，一个秘密科研设施被废弃，无法使用，但里面仍有一些你感兴趣的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的任务是找回 “汞合金”。“汞合金 ”是由一种大规模制造的微生物创造出来的生物，它能够将动物物种合二为一，或者夸大现有物种的特征。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >汞合金是在相互隔离的细胞中制造的。由于所使用的微生物的性质，这些设施必须部分浸没在专门为支持微生物繁殖而制造的液体中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这就是为什么只有船只才能进入，因此这些设施是为海上交通工具的运输和流通而设计的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦产卵，汞齐体就会被捕捉到 F-Pot（专为安全运输而设计的笼子）中。这些笼子会把汞齐关在水下，直到它们启动相关的浮标浮出水面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的飞船配备了能够运输和激活 F-Pot 的起重机，用它来拾取汞齐并将其储存在您的船舱中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >事故发生时，汞齐已被自动安全系统镇静，但不排除有些汞齐仍处于活动状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
